{"id":534,"date":"2007-09-17T09:56:45","date_gmt":"2007-09-17T14:56:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/the_17_sides_of_a_cultural_id.php"},"modified":"2007-09-17T09:56:45","modified_gmt":"2007-09-17T14:56:45","slug":"the_17_sides_of_a_cultural_id","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/the_17_sides_of_a_cultural_id.php","title":{"rendered":"The 17 Sides of a Cultural Identity"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/casa_damusica_logo.gif\" alt=\"Casa da M&uacute;sica Logo, New\" \/><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.oma.eu\/index.php?option=com_projects&#038;view=portal&#038;id=48&#038;Itemid=10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Built in 2005 by Rem Koolhaas&#8217; OMA<\/a> in the city of Porto, Portugal the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.casadamusica.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Casa da M&uacute;sica<\/a> is, without a doubt, a significant architectural statement &mdash; further emphasised by its intense angles and towering presence. By using the building as a visual source, <a href=\"http:\/\/www.sagmeister.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Stefan Sagmeister<\/a> created a dynamic, faceted and endlessly varied identity &mdash; all literally speaking. The resulting logo is perhaps, well, not pretty, but as a vessel for the complete identity and adaptable execution it is a mighty impressive piece of design architecture itself. One on which styles, ideas, themes &mdash; specific or broad &mdash; can be projected upon. Stefan was generous to share this project with us and show what happens behind the scenes in the realization of this identity.<\/p><!--more--><p>\n<img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/casa_damusica_arch.jpg\" alt=\"Casa da M&uacute;sica, by Rem Koolhaas\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"small\"><strong>Casa da M&uacute;sica in Portugal, Porto by Rem Koolhaas.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><br \/><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/divider_entry.gif\" alt=\"---\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/casa_damusica_views.gif\" alt=\"Graphical views of the building\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"small\"><strong>Graphical views of the building.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><br \/><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/divider_entry.gif\" alt=\"---\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/casa_damusica_logo_alts.gif\" alt=\"Alternate logos\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"small\"><strong>From the different views of the building, a system of logos is created.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><br \/><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/divider_entry.gif\" alt=\"---\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/casa_damusica_color_01.jpg\" alt=\"Color\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"small\"><strong>Through the different views of the building, 17 facets are defined &mdash; from those a 17-point color-picking mechanism is created.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><br \/><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/divider_entry.gif\" alt=\"---\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/casa_damusica_color_02.jpg\" alt=\"Color\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"small\"><strong>Need we say that the possibilities are endless?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><br \/><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/divider_entry.gif\" alt=\"---\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/casa_damusica_color_03.jpg\" alt=\"Color Generator\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"small\"><strong>And what would a mutable identity be without its own customized software?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><br \/><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/divider_entry.gif\" alt=\"---\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/casa_damusica_posters_sm.jpg\" alt=\"Applications\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"small\"><strong>To further enhance the felxibility of the identity, the logo can be used in a scary number of freeing ways.<\/strong> [<a href=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/casa_damusica_posters_big.jpg\" onclick=\"window.open('https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/casa_damusica_posters_big.jpg','popup','width=1393,height=664,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0'); return false\">Click here<\/a> for bigger view]<\/span><\/p>\n<p><br \/><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/divider_entry.gif\" alt=\"---\" \/><\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/excerpt_empty.gif\" alt=\"Excerpt Empty\" \/>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"episode_type":"","audio_file":"","duration":"","filesize":"","date_recorded":"","explicit":"","block":"","filesize_raw":""},"categories":[63,12,26],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/534"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=534"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/534\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=534"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=534"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=534"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}